channel.title: Deception-317 release (Current source) | Pk Economy | TokHaar-Kal | 99% RSCombat
channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://img217.imageshack.us/img217/9338/deceptionbannerproject.png[/img]
Hi Moparscape Members, *Note* This is the latest version, not the one that was sold/leaked (Older)! After 1 year of developing Deception with my great Friend AJ (Eliminate) we have decided it's time for it's release. Other than private sales, there has been leaks, there has been leeches. I do not know what else I'll be doing, other than continuing rsps, but I now have a IRL Job, deception was fun but now we can see more of these types of servers instead of remakes, Even I am tired of remakes, we should just push to the future instead of the past. So now I bid you guys good bye with Deception, and I hope you guys enjoy it. I give big credits to Eliminate for letting me use his Server/Client base for Deception, and for all the help he has done to make Deception big when it was in it's prime time. I do highly recommend to use it, as it's great you will have to do very small bug fixes, but this is very well worth it. Only other thing I ask is, if you do use it or even download it just to check it out please give thanks and reputation to Eliminate, who did most of the work. Thanks, Moe.
Media: [CENTER][url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JcfgNV6T3JM&feature=plcp]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JcfgNV6T3JM&feature=plcp[/url][/CENTER] Credits: Aj aka Eliminate - Main developer Moe - Owner/Developer [CENTER]I've decided to release this as Moe and I are done working on Deception. The server was great whilst it lasted and it seemed to be popular due to the sheer fact that it received over 500+ votes within the first week of being launched. [B]If you do appreciate/like or use this release, please show your appreciation by giving the correct credits if/when hosted.[/B] Download: http://dl.dropbox.com/u/89591479/Deception%20release.rar Features - [B]100% Runescape XP Bar 614 Look, Less Lag Perfect Switching Amazing Combat Few Known dupes patched Clipped Following Clipped Combat 634 items. 633 characters. 602 anims including Korasi. 508 maps & objects. New hitmarks like rs Including Criticals. 602 Npc's & Skilltab Fast loading client. Low client memory usage. Full working Curses Items kept on death interface New Shop interface New Bank interface New RS Loading Bar/Login Box/Background New Skill Tab w/ hovering New Friends list/Ignore list[/B] [/CENTER]

item.dc:creator: @Kidpaparoach Kidpaparoach
item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

If people want it I can upload my slightly modified version of this source. I added in some shit so check the notes.

Heres my notes in advance, send me a PM because I probably wont check this thread for a while

added a new stacking system Currency is spirit shards added horrible dicing, percentile only - timers need to be added(very basic) added magic dmg % boosts to stream sol ancient staff chaotic staff ahrims staff, need to add to equipment bonuses Stalls redone + need to change anims (need to add, successfull/fail thiev) has timers. Didn't realise their was already magic dmg % boosts, need to remove one Added antique lamps, code is in.. for some reason buttons on interface dont work. Antiquelamps.java seem fine ids - 2528 6543 10889 11137 11157 14575 14711

added empty command
Censored names, if the name contains a word in the list it’ll be auto banned i.e. love isn’t aloud so if a person made an account called love Me they’d be autobanned(not ip).

Put in some cases for bank booths etc, i.e. varrock banks seers village banks.
Changed ::master to only give combat stats(exluding summoning, hate summoning in rsps always badly done) so that players can skill until the server is fully made into a eco.
Also, going to add in voting which rewards the player according to their total level, don’t want every maxed total haha!

Put old furnace(11666) ontop of edgeville one cause it was pissing me off, timers need to be sorted in smithing.
Added horrible semi-working doors(deletes door temporairly), actionhandler search door to add more -mr extremez
Added working Divine(doesn’t drain prayer, 30% damage reduction) and ely(70% chance of 25% damage reduction).
Changed the korasiDamage formula, not quite like Rs but better than what was implemented.
Added password strengths into client, weak is 4, medium 6, strong 9 - all in client.java to change.

Need to add teles


I think I added in spawning where u pay for what u spawn with shards. Can’t remember and cba checking. These are really bad notes, dw my notes now are much more detailed lul.
